commit message: Initial commit.
Added RootCommands library from https://github.com/dschuermann/superuser-commands.git
Removed unused code and files.
Implemented CertificateManager (including tests).
Added certificate listing with colors to MainActivity.
Added MovedCertificatesStorage, only list moved system certs in GUI.
Added move dialog shown on activity resume.
Updated libsuperuser to reference the main project.
Added move dialog on start and list item buttons (move/delete).
Set correct permissions for moved certificates, added missing test changes.
Don't call blocking functions from ui thread.
Update list automatically when certificates are changed.
Added proper certificate names.
Change coloring (color title instead of whole list item).
Added launcher icon.
Added warning dialog if no root permissions, work around dialogs being shown more than once.
Removed CertificateAdapterTest as class is too interconnected for easy unit testing.
Added progress bar on list items while moving certificate.
Fixed gradle warnings.
Changed app name to 'Move Certs!'.
Added empty text to ListView.
Fixed CertificateAdapter inserting wrong certificate into database.
Added proper gradle release build.
Updated libsuperuser.
Bumped version to 1.0.0.
